Card - Class in edu.cpp.cs.cs141.assignment3
This class represents the abstract notion of a Card, which contatins the attributes of every type of card included in the game.
Card(String) - Constructor for class edu.cpp.cs.cs141.assignment3.Card
This is the default constructor for the class, which requires that every subclass of Card must have a Card.symbol associated with it.
checkMatch(int, int) - Method in class edu.cpp.cs.cs141.assignment3.GameEngine
This method takes two inputs from the user, which are integers that represents a face-down Card in the Grid and compare them by checking symbol values and nullifying them if they're equal.
